<p><b>How to register:</b> We are very non-bureaucratic; we strive to keep things simple. To register, simply show up 15 minutes before any scheduled class and introduce yourself to the instructor or to anyone who appears to know his way around. They'll take care of you from that point. That is all.</p>

<p><a href="http://makatiaikidoclub.com/trainingsched/TrainingSchedule.pdf" target=_blank class=black>Click here to download a printable PDF copy of the training schedule.</a></p>

